# SwiftUI View File Location Rule

All SwiftUI `View` types MUST be located inside the `/Views` directory.

Constraints:
- NEVER create `View` files inside `/Models`, `/Services`, `/Networking`, or `/ViewModels`.
- Every new SwiftUI `View` MUST be created inside `/Views`.
- The file name MUST match the view name.
- Each file SHOULD contain only one primary `View`.

Exception:
The root application entry point that contains the `@main` attribute MUST be placed inside the `/App` directory.
